    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Are you an avid gardener, or just getting started with this outdoor hobby? Every gardener, aspiring or experienced needs a durable and reliable set of gardening gloves! The ToolTreaux garden gloves are a must-have gardening accessory that will help you safely rake leaves, remove thorns, weeding, and plant holes for seeds. Our unique gardening gloves come with durable, high-quality ABS plastic claws that easily attach to the fingertips of the gloves. These claws will assist with the removal of weeds and thorns, and they won’t slip off during gardening activities. In addition to the claws, these garden gloves feature an elastic cuff that will stretch to comfortably fit most adult hands, making this an ideal pair of gloves for both men and women alike</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ToolTreaux Essential Gardening Tools and Cultivating Accessories (Many Options)</h2>\n  <p>Are you an avid gardener, or just getting started with this outdoor hobby? Every gardener, aspiring or experienced needs a durable and reliable set of gardening gloves! The ToolTreaux garden gloves are a must-have gardening accessory that will help you safely rake leaves, remove thorns, weeding, and plant holes for seeds.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>1 PAIR GARDEN GLOVES - ToolTreaux garden gloves are a must-have pair of protective gear for all gardeners; Use them to safely rake leaves, dig holes for planting, remove thorns, and weeding to keep your garden and yard beautiful</li>\n    <li>STURDY ABS CLAWS - Unique gardening gloves come with durable, high-quality ABS plastic claws that will assist with the removal of weeds and dangerous plant materials; Sturdy claws won’t slip off during gardening</li>\n    <li>ONE SIZE FITS MOST - Garden gloves feature an elastic cuff that will stretch to fit most hands, ideal for both men and women gardeners; Latex material of gloves is weather-resistant so you can count on them to protect your hands rain or shine</li>\n    <li>PUNCTURE RESISTANT - Gardening gloves are designed to be puncture resistant so you can use them in gardening beds and thorny bushes without worry; Comes in bright green color for high visibility with black fingertips</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Materials:</strong> ABS plastic (claws), Latex, and elastic (gloves); Colors: black/green; Size: one size fits most (stretchy); Puncture-resistant: yes; Weather-resistant: yes</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/home/garden/tooltreaux_gloves_26C-GGLOVES-HM-75966-96_1PAIR_main_pl.jpg\" alt=\"Are you an avid gardener, or just getting started with this outdoor hobby\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> GGLVTT</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810131702533</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Multicolor</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Our unique gardening gloves come with durable, high-quality ABS plastic claws that easily attach to the fingertips of the gloves. These claws will assist with the removal of weeds and thorns, and they won’t slip off during gardening activities.</p>\n  <p>In addition to the claws, these garden gloves feature an elastic cuff that will stretch to comfortably fit most adult hands, making this an ideal pair of gloves for both men and women alike. The latex material of the gloves is both weather and puncture resistant, so you can count on them to protect your hands rain or shine. These gloves are a great gift idea for yourself or any other gardening enthusiast in your life!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
